    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "**Câu 2.** Cho hình lăng trụ $ABC.A_1B_1C_1$. Gọi $G_1$ là trọng tâm tam giác $A_1B_1C_1$. Khi đó:"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      217,
      909,
      536,
      1282
    ],
    "category": "Picture"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      212,
      1291,
      616,
      1368
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "A. $\\overrightarrow{AG_1} = \\overrightarrow{AA_1} + \\frac{1}{3}(\\overrightarrow{AB} + \\overrightarrow{AC})$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      862,
      1291,
      1288,
      1368
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "B. $\\overrightarrow{AG_1} = \\frac{1}{3}\\overrightarrow{AA_1} + \\frac{2}{3}(\\overrightarrow{AB} + \\overrightarrow{AC})$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      212,
      1377,
      614,
      1454
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "C. $\\overrightarrow{AG_1} = \\frac{1}{3}(\\overrightarrow{AA_1} + \\overrightarrow{AB} + \\overrightarrow{AC})$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      862,
      1377,
      1274,
      1454
    ],
    "category": "List-item",
    "text": "D. $\\overrightarrow{AG_1} = \\overrightarrow{AA_1} + \\frac{2}{3}(\\overrightarrow{AB} + \\overrightarrow{AC})$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      833,
      1463,
